  "name": "Morrison COU1 — CPB hemolysis credibility assessment (MRL 3)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under cardiopulmonary bypass (CPB) conditions. This package re-evaluates COU1 at Model Risk Level 3 following a regulatory query regarding worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for a Class II CPB device. Twelve of thirteen credibility factors are fully assessed and meet or exceed required levels. The Equivalency of input parameters factor is characterised in the narrative as not applicable to this COU because the validation experiment used the same pump geometry as the computational model; however, the factor is encoded with factorStatus 'not-assessed' rather than 'not-applicable', leaving a material gap at MRL 3.",
