      "rationale": "SST k-omega turbulence model selected based on published FDA benchmark study comparisons (Hariharan et al. 2011). Giersiepen-Wurzinger hemolysis power-law model validated against literature erythrocyte fragility data. Model form uncertainty estimated at ±12% NIH via sensitivity study across three turbulence model variants."
