      "rationale": "Blood viscosity (3.5 mPa·s) and density (1060 kg/m³) sourced from ASTM F1841 reference fluid specifications. Pump geometry digitised from coordinate measuring machine data (±0.02 mm). One-at-a-time sensitivity study confirms NIH sensitivity to viscosity ±5% is less than 3% NIH change."
