      "rationale": "Validation experiments used ASTM F1841-compliant blood analogue fluid (glycerol-water, viscosity matched). Pump specimen manufactured to drawing tolerances; CMM report on file. Three repeat runs at each operating point; coefficient of variation < 4% for NIH measurements."
