      "rationale": "The validation experiment was conducted using the same nominal pump geometry as the computational model, and the blood analogue fluid properties were matched to the CFD boundary conditions. Because the experimental and simulation configurations share an identical geometric definition and fluid specification, the assessment team concluded that a formal equivalency evaluation does not apply to this COU and that no additional quantitative comparison of input parameters is warranted. Accordingly, this factor has not been formally assessed against a required gradation level."
